 ree of charge!  At our CONNECT event\, you will: Connect with women who ar
 e serious about growing their business and generous about sharing their ex
 perience. Be celebrated for your accomplishments\, and leave with the conf
 idence to aim even higher. Expand your visibility in SLO County while tapp
 ing into a national network. It's North County energy with a national reac
 h. We never apologize for being ambitious about our business here!  Locati
