 acoustic to screaming\, electric guitar soloing in front of a rock band to
  her dynamic one woman band using loops\, beatboxing and a healthy case of
  ADHD to her advantage.\n\n \n\nFord’s Righteous Babe Records debut was 
 produced by Ani Difranco\, mixed by John Driskell Hopkins \\(Zac Brown Ban
 d\\) and is set to release early 2025. Kristen is endorsed by Gallagher Gu
 itars\, K&K pickups & G7th Capos
