UID:2604012PeoIrVgQk6E5GE-HNAtGw
DESCRIPTION:Friday night stand-up comedy in Downtown Santa Rosa\n\nVIP TAB
 LES NOW AVAILABLE! Snag a table for 4 with preferred seating\, your own pr
 ivate call button to summon service\, and your first round of drinks (or a
  bottle of wine) for only $95!\n\nEvery Friday night hilarious comedians f
 rom The Bay Area and beyond perform at Barrel Proof Lounge. Stick around a
 fter for late-night karaoke! Fresh lineup of funny each Friday.\n\nThis We
 ek: Casey Williams (host) Bryan Bayley Iris Benson Headliner: Marcus Howar
 d\n\nBorn and raised in Oakland\, Marcus Howard is a comedian who’s been
  making audiences laugh for years. With a sharp wit and a unique perspecti
 ve on life\, Marcus has become a regular on the Bay Area comedy scene.\n\n
 He performs regularly with Don’t Tell Comedy and the Alameda Comedy Club
 \, and his comedy touches on everything from kids to race to relationships
 . Marcus is known for his ability to turn everyday situations into hilario
 us stories\, and he’s not afraid to tackle tough topics with humor and h
 eart. Whether he’s riffing on the absurdities of being a liberal or shar
 ing his thoughts on the state of the world\, Marcus is always entertaining
 \, insightful\, and funny. IG: @marcushoweird\n\n21+ Doors - 7p / Show - 8
 p $15adv / $20door\n\nCheck out **www.BarrelProofLounge.com** for all so
 rts of good times ahead.
LOCATION:Barrel Proof Lounge
URL:https://www.eventbrite.com/e/friday-night-comedy-marcus-howard-downtow
 n-santa-rosa-tickets-1982249826592?aff=oddtdtcreator
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
