DESCRIPTION:ABOUT CLAY BELL\n\nBorn into a musical family\, Clay first had
  a taste of performing at the age of 5 when his parents band went on tour.
  He has since toured extensively throughout Northern America\, Europe\, In
 donesia as well as Greenland and the Caribbean. Clay has shared the stage 
 with: Ciaran Gribbin \\(INXS\\)\, Mark McGrath \\(Sugar Ray\\)\, Bret Mic
 haels \\(Poison\\)\, Lou Gramm \\(Foreigner\\)\, Mickey Thomas \\(Jefferso
 n Starship\\)\, the Sugarhill Gang and shared bills with: Alex Chilton \\(
 Big Star\\)\, The Posies\, Cracker\, Earth Wind and Fire\, Colin Hay \\(Me
 n at Work\\)\, The Church and many\, many others. Clay continues to hone h
 is craft wether he is playing with the high-energy cover band Pop Rocks\, 
 Bell & Co \\(his trio\\) or his acoustic solo act.
