UID:260312X8KTFwvt4UeKxpn3IsT2Bw
DESCRIPTION:Groovesters!\n\n 🎸🌟 Get ready to groove with us at The S
 uisun Valley Filling Station in Fairfield! 🎶 Join The Groovy Judy Band 
 for a soul-stirring live performance on Friday\, April 10\, 2026\, from 4:
 00pm to 7:00pm!\n\n🎵 Settle in with a beer or wine and let the music mo
 ve you as we bring our groovy vibe to Fairfield. From funky beats to class
 ic tunes\, we're all set to make your afternoon fun and enjoyable!\n\nFrid
 ay\, April 10\n\nThe Groovy Judy Band  \n\nThe Suisun Valley Filling Stati
 on \n\n2529 Mankas Corner Rd. \n\nFairfield\, CA 94534\n\n4:00pm - 7:00pm\
 n\n21\\+ FREE
