DESCRIPTION:Join Genesis House\, Sustainable Solano and the Vallejo Enviro
 nmental Leadership Fellowship to help plant trees\, improve air quality an
 d expand Vallejo's green spaces.\n\nWe will be planting trees at Genesis t
 o beautify the garden\, purify polluted air\, create shade\, and provide a
  barrier along the highway. We will also be planting a garden to grow food
  & create a pollinator habitat.\n\nParticipants will also have the opportu
 nity to share about the locations and resources they love in Vallejo to he
 lp build community resilience!\n\nLunch and other refreshments will be pro
