BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Vallejo Yacht Club Opening Day
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260411T120000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260411T170000
UID:260407NxryFlSFGkGQnD6qFgZYmA
DESCRIPTION:Come down and experience a traditional opening day of the boat
 ing season celebration.\n\nBeginning at noon and running to 5:00 PM \, tho
 se that love boats and being by the water can enjoy many of the traditiona
 l opening day activities. Following the blessing of the fleet parade\, vis
 it the Vallejo Yacht Club for their Open House. There will be games for ad
 ults and children. If you are young or still young at heart you will enjoy
  watching and participating in some of our on and off the water games. whi
 ch runs from the end of the parade until 9:00 PM. Between noon and 1:30 we
  will have hotdogs and soft drinks for sale.\n\nFor more than 125 years\, 
 the Vallejo Yacht Club has been an institution in the local community and 
 the greater San Francisco Bay boating community. The club is a wonderful p
 lace to gather on the waterfront\, build lasting friendships\, and enjoy a
  wide variety of social activities and watersports.\n\nMembers enjoy a ful
 l calendar of racing and boating events. Membership includes both boat own
 ers and those who simply enjoy being around the water. The club offers sai
 ling lessons and maintains a fleet of club-owned sailboats for members to 
 use. Vallejo Yacht Club is one of the few clubs on the Bay that owns its m
 arina and regularly dredges it. The marina features a newly built seawall\
 , reconstructed docks\, and about 125 slips of various sizes. It is truly 
 a fun and inviting place to spend time.
LOCATION:Vallejo Yacht Club
URL:https://bohemian.com/events-calendar/#/details/vallejo-yacht-club-open
 ing-day/18374358/2026-04-11T12
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
