 eel something real. Whether you come to be inspired\, to vibe\, or to conn
 ect — this is your space. Special performances fron seasoned and upcomin
 g artists alike!\n\nWith headlining performances from singer/songwriter du
 o HOUS3 and CANDID!!\n\nRaw. Authentic. Unforgettable.\n\nJoin us for an e
 vening where art speaks louder than anything else.\n\n$20 entry at the doo
 r. Please arrive early as this will be a limited space event!\n\nAges 16 a
 nd up are permitted to attend.
