UID:2604018r4sbd4wlU-hbZiZ-pZY6w
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a special Saturday acoustic live music set at Adob
 e Road Winery in Downtown Petaluma. Sip on award-winning wines while enjo
 ying talented local musicians in a warm and inviting atmosphere. Choose fr
 om wines by the glass or bottle to discover new favorites. Reserve your sp
 ot on Tock and make it a memorable night of great music\, fine wine\, an
 d good company!\n\nDavid Correa is a celebrated guitarist and composer ble
 nding Latin rhythms with Spanish and world music influences. Since 1999\, 
 The David Correa Group has built a loyal fanbase across the Bay Area and b
 eyond with energetic\, rhythm-driven performances. The group has toured ex
 tensively throughout the western U.S. and earned multiple accolades\, incl
 uding three consecutive NORBAY Awards for Best Latin Band. Correa has rele
 ased seven albums\, including New Moon and Alta Vista\, and has been fe
 atured alongside New Flamenco greats like Ottmar Liebert and Jesse Cook. H
 is live shows promise a vibrant mix of soulful guitar\, rhythm\, and music
 al storytelling.
LOCATION:Adobe Road Winery
URL:https://adoberoadwines.com/events/live-music-david-correa-april-11-202
 6/
