 ogether. \n\nJoin us every Saturday from 3–6 PM at Spicy Vines for a tas
 ting room experience like no other — where top local musicians from acro
 ss the Bay Area meet our award-winning small-lot wines. From Rock & Roll a
 nd Blues to Jazz\, Bluegrass\, and Americana\, each weekend brings new sou
 nds and new reasons to raise a glass. \n\nQuintessence Music Duo Quintess
 ence is a married musical duo whose shared passion for performing and song
 writing creates a warm\, reflective soundscape that celebrates both the or
 dinary and the extraordinary. \n\nDetails\n\nNo cover. Walk-ins are welco
 me\, but this event tends to fill up quickly\, so we recommend making a re
 servation. We are dog and family friendly!
