 ins will be taken if space is available. Ages 16 and up need to have a val
 id California Fishing License. For more information\, please visit the web
 site listed above. Sign up for a time slot starting Wednesday\, March 4\, 
 2025 at  novato.org/regforfun \\(Only children need to register\, supervis
 ing adults do not. Please limit signups to no more than two children per a
 dult.\\) 8:00 - 8:45 8:15 - 9:00 8:30 - 9:15 8:45 - 9:30 9:00 - 9:45 9:15 
