DESCRIPTION:Join **Sing Napa Valley** for its annual spring choral concert
 \, *Around the World in 80 Minutes*\, an uplifting celebration of cultures
 \, languages\, and the music that connects us all. Conducted by **Ronnie Z
 anella**\, the choir brings the world to life through powerful songs in 9+
  languages\, including Portuguese\, Zulu\, Hebrew\, Russian\, Lakota\, and
  Mandarin and more.\n\nFeel the joy\, longing\, and hope woven into each p
 iece. Be inspired by music that reminds us how deeply connected we are —
  across borders\, cultures\, and generations. This is more than a concert\
 ; it’s an experience you’ll carry with you long after the final note.\
 n\n🎟 **Reserve your seat now and travel the world through song:** 👉 
 https://www.zeffy.com/en-US/ticketing/around-the-world-in-80-minutes\n\n
 ℹ️ **Learn more:** https://www.singnapavalley.org\n\n*Processing fees 
 are optional.*
LOCATION:Napa Methodist Church 
URL:https://www.zeffy.com/en-US/ticketing/around-the-world-in-80-minutes
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
