 cover the joys of unplugged living. Join Tex\, Phonicia\, and their parent
 s on a laugh-out-loud journey that reminds us that sometimes the best conn
 ections don't need Wi-Fi.\n\n**Time:** 11am - 12pm\n\n**Location:** Usher 
