 rt\, part history lesson\, this high-octane journey celebrates the artists
  who shaped American music with powerhouse vocals\, storytelling\, and irr
 esistible rhythm.\n\nJuke Joint Jukebox features the vocal talents of Gar
 y Stanford Jr.\, Bradley Kynard\, Skylaer Palacios\, Sharon Griffith\, Sol
 ona Husband\, Julie Dormire and Leo Kimuyu. They are joined by pianist Vic
 tor Hall\, guitarist Greg Call\, and drummer Lance Lee.\n\nFilled with soa
 ring songs\, poignant storytelling and live music\, Juke Joint Jukebox is
  a special event not to be missed!
