SUMMARY:KWMR's 'Cultivating Place' Live! with radio-host Jennifer Jewell
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260412T140000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260412T140000
UID:260328ZGrgfi6koECMAIDmElFDLg
DESCRIPTION:Jennifer Jewell’s popular podcast ***"Cultivating Place\,"**
 * explores ‘natural history and the human impulse to garden.” KWMR Com
 munity Radio is proud to air it Saturday mornings from 8-9 AM on the West 
 Marin airwaves\, and we are *very* excited to announce that we’ll be hos
 ting Jennifer Jewell in person for a **live taping of her show**! \n\nPle
 ase join KWMR for **“Cultivating Place LIVE\,”** an interactive\, gard
 en-focused event benefitting KWMR\, at **The Dance Palace Community Center
 ** in Point Reyes Station\, on **Sunday\, April 12th.**\n\nDoors open at *
 *2 PM** for mingling and a **seed swap with West Marin Climate Action.** B
 ring your extra seeds and starts down\, to mix & match with fellow gardene
 rs and cultivators…while enjoying snacks and local tea!\n\nThen at **3 P
 M**\, when we’ll be doing a live taping of **Jennifer Jewell’s convers
 ation with Rebecca Newburn** - seed conservationist\, and co-founder of th
 e Richmond Seed Lending Library. Stick around after the talk for more ming
 ling with fellow nature-enthusiasts. \n\n**Tickets are on sale at kwmr.or
 g.** This event is sliding scale\, $10-$50\, and all proceeds provide "see
 d funding" to fertilize KWMR’s upcoming Spring Pledge Drive\, happening 
 April 18th through May 1st. Please choose the ticket price that feels righ
 t for you\, or buy yours at the door! \n\n***Thank you to our generous Ev
 ent Sponsors:*** • Bolinas Hardware • Commonweal New School • Gather
 ing Thyme • Inverness Garden Club of West Marin • Larner Seeds • Mot
 el Inverness • Point Reyes Lavender Company.\n\n*Thank you for your supp
 ort of homegrown radio - see you on April 12th!*
LOCATION:Dance Palace Community Center
URL:https://secure.qgiv.com/for/cultivatingplacelive/event/cultivatingplac
 elive/
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
