UID:260319LxkOEZSk60KwEX8JhWqghA
DESCRIPTION:Ready to dance? Join our beginner salsa class where no experie
 nce or partner is needed. Just comfortable shoes and desire to have fun!\n
 \nGreat for first timers!\n\nNo dance experience required\n\nNon-marking s
 hoes soles\n\nNo partner necessary\n\nOur relaxed environment is perfect f
 or learning salsa basics\, as we make it fun and enjoyable. In this class 
 you will learn basic directional steps\, proper frame for partner-work and
  simple turn patterns. We organize our curriculum so that the movements ar
 e easy to remember. Join us to learn the fundamentals! No experience is ne
 cessary and no partner is required. Drop-in fee is $20.\n\nDate & Time: Tu
 esdays @ 5:30PM – 6:30PM\n\nAddress: 4140 Redwood Highway \\#8 San Rafae
 l\, CA\n\nNote: Arrive 10 minutes before. No floor marking shoe soles allo
 wed.
LOCATION:Salsa Dance Marin
