 e life and philosophy of Thoreau: nonviolent resistance\, environmental st
 ewardship\, and civic responsibility.\n\nFollowing the screening\, stay fo
 r a panel discussion that brings Thoreau’s ideas into today’s world wi
 th journalist and activist Greg King - who is featured on NorCal’s Emmy 
