BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Quantum Coherence with Anistara Ma Ka
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260416T203000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260416T203000
UID:26033170stKvSr-km5_Op_CNa-5A
DESCRIPTION:A Guided Energy Alignment Experience\n\nQuantum Coherence is a
  powerful\, immersive meditation experience designed to bring your mind\, 
 body\, and energy field into alignment.\n\nGuided live by Anistara Ma Ka\,
  this journey is a channeled transmission—drawing from years of personal
  practice and devotion to energetic mastery\, meditation\, and consciousne
 ss work.\n\nInspired by the teachings of pioneers such as Dr. Joe Dispenza
 \, Tony Robbins\, and Regan Hillyer\, this experience weaves together scie
 nce\, spirituality\, and somatic awareness into a grounded\, accessible\, 
 and deeply transformative practice.\n\n- Each session is unique and intuit
 ively guided  \n\n\\\\= Experience a blend of breathwork\, visualization\
 , and energetic alignment\n\n- Drop out of overthinking and into embodied 
 presence\n\n- Activate coherence between heart\, mind\, and body\n\n- Ampl
 ified within the powerful field of the Energy Enhancement System\n\nWith c
 arefully curated soundscapes and frequency-rich music supporting the journ
 ey\, you’ll be held in a multidimensional environment designed to help y
 ou release\, recalibrate\, and reconnect.\n\nThis is not a recording. This
  is a live transmission.\n\nA space where you don’t just meditate… you
  become the frequency of wholeness.\n\nAbout Anistara\n\nAnistara Ma Ka is
  a multidimensional guide\, best-selling author\, and transformational spe
 aker devoted to supporting awakening souls in remembering who they truly a
 re.\n\nAs the Founder of Ascension University and the Mother of 11.11 Unif
 ied\, she guides individuals into embodied leadership\, sovereignty\, and 
 alignment with New Earth consciousness through her teachings\, transmissio
 ns\, and ceremonial work.\n\nAn ordained Sacred Portal Oracle of the Porta
 l Priestess Mystery School and steward of Joy Oasis\, Anistara creates imm
 ersive retreats\, initiations\, and ceremonies rooted in ancient wisdom an
 d modern embodiment. Her work weaves energetic leadership\, sacred remembr
 ance\, and lived devotion—holding spaces where transformation unfolds na
 turally and participants reconnect with their purpose\, presence\, and inn
 er authority.
LOCATION:Energy Wave Center
URL:https://energywavecenter.com/anistara/
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
