DESCRIPTION:Nancy Fawson is a powerhouse Bay Area-based vocalist and songw
 riter whose musical roots run deep in soul\, R&B and rock. Raised on the i
 conic sounds of Sam Cooke\, Etta James\, Aretha Franklin\, Chaka Khan\, St
 evie Wonder\, and Amy Winehouse\, Nancy’s musical influences have left a
 n indelible imprint on her voice and style. With a unique\, soulful tone a
 nd a passion for heartfelt expression\, Nancy connects with her audience o
 n a profound level—delivering each song with purity\, emotion\, and auth
 enticity.\n\nNancy’s vocal range spans across a variety of genres\, incl
 uding soul\, funk\, blues\, R&B\, and rock\, allowing her to bring versati
 lity to every performance. Whether performing with a duo or full band\, sh
 e engages audiences with her compelling stage presence and soulful deliver
 y.\n\nAs the lead singer of the popular Marin-based blues\, soul\, and fun
 k band Corner Pocket\, Nancy continues to captivate crowds with her raw en
 ergy and dedication to the craft. In addition to live performances\, she i
 s also available for recording session work\, offering her talents as both
  a lead and background vocalist.\n\nWith a sound that blends classic influ
 ences with modern flair\, Nancy Fawson is an artist whose voice you won’
 t soon forget.
LOCATION:Brewsters Beer Garden
URL:https://www.bandsintown.com/e/107881708?app_id=pkvts0on0m&came_from=28
 7&utm_medium=api&utm_source=partner_api&utm_campaign=event
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
