 ir clothing with woven darning—a functional and beautiful technique espe
 cially suited for knitwear. This workshop covers material selection\, sett
 ing up a darn\, and weaving strong\, expressive patches.\n\nIn this worksh
 op you’ll:\n\n• Choose yarns and materials for woven darning\n\n• Se
 t up and weave a stable darn\n\n• Explore design choices for creative\, 
 visible repairs\n\nBring a garment to mend\, or use provided samples.Mater
 ials included\; no experience required.
