 eates a lofty\, reversible fabric that looks complex but becomes rhythmic 
 once you understand the structure.\n\nIn this workshop you’ll:\n\n• Le
 arn the basics of brioche knitting\n\n• Practice brioche knit \\(BRK\\) 
 and brioche purl \\(BRP\\)\n\n• Work two-color brioche in the round\n\n
