DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260418T220000
UID:260331g5K_dBOKV0uzPbMsd5S4Qg
DESCRIPTION:The Roaring 420’s: Great Gatsby Party\n\nStep into a world o
 f decadence\, indulgence\, and elevated highs at Mercy’s Roaring 420’s
  Gatsby Costume Party—a fully immersive 1920s-inspired cannabis experien
 ce inside The Lounge.\n\nOn Saturday\, April 18th from 6PM – 10PM\, we
 ’re transforming the space into a lavish Gatsby-era affair where luxury 
 meets smoke-filled sophistication. Velvet nights\, golden details\, and ja
 zz-era energy set the tone—brought to life by a live performance from Fo
 g City Swing\, delivering a one-of-a-kind soundtrack of classic swing\, mo
 dern hits\, and big band flair. Their signature “smallest big band” so
 und creates an electric\, dance-worthy atmosphere you won’t find anywher
 e else.\n\nYour ticket includes a full dinner experience\, a curated good
 ie bag\, and your own assigned seat—so you can settle in and enjoy the n
 ight in style.\n\nThis isn’t just a party—it’s an experience.\n\nSip
  on herbal cannabis-infused cocktails\, explore interactive brand statio
 ns\, and indulge in guided tasting options designed to elevate your palat
 e. Watch the craft come alive at our live joint rolling area\, try your l
 uck with casino-style games\, and discover curated moments of entertainme
 nt throughout the night.\n\nAnd of course—dress to impress.\n\nWe’re h
 osting a Gatsby Costume Contest\, so come in your finest flapper dresses\
 , sharpest suits\, and boldest 1920s looks for a chance to stand out and t
 ake the spotlight for the night.\n\nThis is a fully immersive themed expe
 rience\, and guests are highly encouraged to participate in the dress code
  to bring the night to life.\n\nDate & Time\n\nDate: Saturday\, April 18\,
  2026\n\nTime: 6:00 - 10:00 PM\n\nTicket Tiers\n\n🎷 $100 Reserved Insid
 e Seating Ticket. Perfect for guests who want premium comfort and a front-
 row seat to the night’s festivities. Enjoy the full Gatsby treatment wit
 h reserved indoor seating in the heart of the action. Ticket includes: gou
 rmet dinner\, exclusive goodie bag & access to the immersive Roaring 420
 ’s experience\n\n🌿 $75 Open Outside Seating Ticket. Ideal for a more 
 relaxed\, social vibe under the night sky. Soak in the atmosphere with ope
 n outdoor seating while still enjoying all the indulgences of the evening.
  Ticket includes: gourmet dinner\, exclusive goodie bag & access to the im
 mersive Roaring 420’s experience\n\n21\\+ Only | DCC \\# C12-0000420-LIC
LOCATION:The Lounge at Mercy
URL:https://www.themercylounge.com
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
