BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Calistoga Art Center's Annual Souper Bowl #16
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260418T173000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260418T210000
UID:260303ou6k6cyISEG_DvHoM0-rLQ
DESCRIPTION:CALISTOGA (February 21\, 2026) – Now in its 16th year\, Cali
 stoga Art Center’s popular Souper Bowl fundraiser will be held on Saturd
 ay\, April 18\, at the Boys & Girls Club of Calistoga.  Tickets are now o
 n sale\, and event sponsorships are available.\n\nSouper Bowl gets its nam
 e from the unique pairing of gourmet soups from local restaurants with han
 dmade ceramic bowls crafted by CAC’s talented instructors and students. 
 Guests choose from over 250 artisan bowls which they take home at the end 
 of the evening. Many prize their collection of bowls from past events. Eac
 h year\, Souper Bowl guests vote for their favorite soup of the night. Las
 t year’s winner was Lovina for its luscious asparagus bisque. \n\nSoupe
 r Bowl 2026 will be more exciting than ever. Guests will bid on a dazzling
  collection of live and silent auction items as well as enjoy Calistoga AV
 A wines and desserts. Here’s a “taste” of the items up for auction: 
 A staycation at a private residence at the Four Seasons\; a private Sip & 
 Paint party at Calistoga Art Center\, curated wine collections and tasting
 s\, special dining experiences\, fine art and craft pieces in various medi
 a\, and more.\n\nProceeds from the event will directly support ongoing art
  programs for the community\, including those designed for children\, teen
 s\, and seniors. Funds raised will also help cover administrative expenses
  to operate the CAC as well as critical capital improvements to its facili
 ty. \n\nTickets are $125 each and available online at www.calistogaartcen
 ter.org/events or by calling 707-942-2278. Each event ticket includes a ha
 ndmade ceramic bowl to take home\, an unlimited soup tasting\, charcuterie
 \, bread\, and cookies. Wine tickets will be available for purchase. Each 
 guest will be assigned a designated table to ensure smooth and organized s
 eating and you can request seating with friends.  Creative center pieces 
 and table numbers will be designed by CAC students.
LOCATION:Calistoga Boys & Girls Club
URL:https://calistogaartcenter.org/souper-bowl-2026
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
