UID:260401IrpBBuKoWk2A3TTQ6FWVIQ
DESCRIPTION:Directions:\n\nMeet at the gate on San Carlos Way in Novato. F
 rom Hwy 101 in Novato\, take the exit for San Marin Dr west 2.1 miles. Tur
 n right onto San Carlos Way and follow to end \\(dead end\\).\n\nSponsor: 
 Parks\n\nAccommodation Information: If you are a person with a disability 
 and require an accommodation to participate in a County program\, service\
 , or activity\, requests may be made by calling 415-473-4381 \\( Voice\\)\
 , Dial 711 for CA Relay\, or by submitting a\n\nDisability Accommodation R
 equest\n\nat least five business days in advance of the event. We will do 
 our best to fulfill requests received with less than five business days' n
 otice. Copies of documents are available in alternative formats upon reque
 st.\n\nJoin a ranger for a challenging hike to the quarry at the summit of
  Mt. Burdell. We will begin our journey at the base of the mountain and fo
 llow the Old Quarry Trail to the top. Along the way\, we'll discuss the hi
 story of the Gallag her Quarry. This hike is strenuous\, covering approxim
 ately 6.2 miles with an elevation gain of about 1\,300 feet. Appropriate f
 or teenagers and adults. Friendly dogs are welcome but must be on leash. D
 ress in layers and wear sturdy shoes. Adverse weather or poor air quality 
 may cancel. Call \\(415\\) 473- 2816 two hours before the event to confirm
  the status. Registration is required.\n\nQuestions: Contact\n\nAlec Gueri
 n
URL:http://www.trumba.com/https://www%20.marincounty.gov/disability-accomm
 odation-request
