DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260419T110000
UID:2604076-gZPG3jXUSuW97TKTbFQQ
DESCRIPTION:Join Rooted Vallejo and volunteers from Vallejo Run Club \\(an
 d get a FREE small smoothie offered by Sunshine Smoothies!!!\\) during a f
 un day of beautifying our city! We'll be gathering at Sunshine Smoothies a
 nd cleaning up the trail along the wetlands and Wilson Ave. Join us! Get o
 utside\, meet cool people\, and make a real difference in our community.\n
 \nLocation:\n\nWe’ll start at Sunshine Smoothies on Wilson Ave. \\(maybe
  grabbing a tasty treat?\\) and work our way around the wetlands and the N
 apa Valley Vine Trail along Wilson Ave.\n\nParking:\n\nFind parking near S
 unshine Smoothies and street parking along Wilson Ave.\n\nWhat We Do:\n\nI
 f you've never been to a cleanup before: Welcome! We're a group of Vallejo
  residents cleaning up some of the city's dirtiest walkways and paths\, on
 e section at a time. We work with the City of Vallejo\, which provides too
 ls\, equipment\, and trash bags\, and we gather once a month to pick up tr
 ash and beautify a small section of town. It's easy\, fun\, and the result
 s are immediate. Learn more about us at www.rootedvallejo.com!
LOCATION:Sunshine Smoothies
URL:https://www.eventbrite.com/e/rooted-vallejo-cleanup-wetlands-wilson-av
 e-tickets-1986437136950
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
