DESCRIPTION:Bingo Smokeout: Reefer Madness Edition\n\nNumbers. Prizes. Ele
 vated Vibes.\n\nOn Sunday\, April 19th from 10AM – 6PM\, step into a hig
 h-energy twist on a classic favorite inside The Lounge at Mercy.\n\nThis i
 sn’t your average bingo.\n\nThis is bingo—elevated.\n\nCards in hand. 
 Smoke in the air. Energy in the room.\n\nPlay through multiple bingo round
 s throughout the day\, compete for prizes\, and stay locked into an experi
 ence that blends cannabis culture with interactive gameplay from start to 
 finish.\n\nYour ticket includes access to all bingo sessions\, one handcra
 fted herbal cocktail\, brand tastings\, exclusive product drops\, and addi
 tional games and activations happening across the space.\n\nBetween rounds
 \, explore\, connect\, and keep the momentum going—this is a full-day ex
 perience built for 420 weekend.\n\nOne game. All day.\n\nLet the numbers h
 it.\n\nThis is a 420-friendly interactive experience hosted inside our ful
 ly licensed cannabis consumption lounge\, where guests can enjoy responsib
 ly while participating in gameplay\, tastings\, and activations. Bingo hit
 s different here.\n\nTicket Tier\n\n$25 — General Admission\n\nEntry to 
 Bingo Smokeout 🎱\n\nIncludes access to all bingo rounds\, one herbal co
 cktail\, brand tastings\, games\, and product drops.\n\n21\\+ Only | DCC \
 \# C12-0000420-LIC
LOCATION:The Lounge at Mercy
URL:https://www.themercylounge.com
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
