 speaker or just starting to learn\, this is a perfect way to practice Span
 ish in a relaxed\, wine-filled setting.   Cost: $15 \\(\\+ tax\\) per per
 son •    Includes one glass of wine or zero-proof verjus spritz •  
   2 rounds of Loteria •    Chances to win prizes\n\nAdditional wine p
 urchases available Empanadas available for $15 \\(\\+ tax\\)   No Spanish
  experience necessary - come ready to learn\, laugh\, and enjoy some delic
 ious wine!\n\nWalk-ins welcome based on availability. Please allow up to 3
 0 minutes for empanadas\, preorders recommended.
LOCATION:Keller Estate
