BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Planning an Event with Ease (Really!)
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260419T140000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260419T163000
UID:260408rpXll1DLikC1NwhtOI1TEA
DESCRIPTION:In today’s world\, most of us want more ways to connect with
  each other. However\, hosting an event can feel stressful! Whether you e
 ntertain at home\, plan meetings\, events\, or have a major celebration on
  the horizon\, this workshop will lower your planning anxiety and help you
  create a glorious end result. Just as cooking is about planning with ste
 ps and a process to follow\, it's the same with events. Come learn the rec
 ipe and the secrets that make every event a joy to plan and produce. \n
 \nThis workshop is for people who:\n\nLove to entertain and want more help
  to make it easier\n\nFind it stressful and are nervous to entertain\n\nDo
 n’t entertain but would like to\n\nDuring this 2.5-hour interactive work
 shop you will gain information\, be able to ask questions and discover a n
 ew way of thinking about event design – which is looking holistically at
  any gathering. You will be surprised at what you will learn!\n\nThe book\
 , *Everything is an Event\, A Step-by-Step Guide Creating Memorable Occas
 ions for Today’s Lifestyle* is included with the class and shares ho
 w to design and plan events with greater ease\, more order\, more fun and 
 no stress.
LOCATION:Book Passage\, Corte Madera
URL:https://www.bookpassage.com/event/planning-event-ease-really-marinda-f
 reeman
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
