DESCRIPTION:Tea &amp\; Tarot &bull\; Grounded Growth Edition\n\nEarth ener
 gy governs stability\, resources\, value\, embodiment\, and what we are he
 re to build in the material world. In this Earth-themed Tea &amp\; Tarot g
 athering\, we focus on business\, livelihood\, prosperity\, and sustainabl
 e growth &mdash\; not through hustle or pressure\, but through alignment\,
  structure\, and embodied worth.\n\nThis experience is designed for entrep
 reneurs\, creatives\, and anyone in a season of building. Tarot is used as
  a reflective tool to explore your relationship with money\, work\, and lo
 ng-term vision\, helping you clarify what wants to take root and what need
 s stronger foundations.\n\nWhat We'll Explore\n\n    &bull\;    Your curre
 nt relationship with money\, work\, and value\n\n    &bull\;    Where ener
 gy is supporting growth &mdash\; and where it may be leaking\n\n    &bull\
 ;    Structures\, boundaries\, or systems that want refinement\n\n    &bul
 l\;    How to grow prosperity in ways that feel ethical\, sustainable\, an
 d embodied\n\nWhat's Included\n\n    &bull\;    A grounding opening to anc
 hor intention and presence\n\n    &bull\;    Individual tarot pulls focuse
 d on business and material flow\n\n    &bull\;    Practical reflection pro
 mpts you can apply immediately\n\n    &bull\;    Tea service to support ne
 rvous system regulation and clarity\n\nThis is not about quick fixes or fi
 nancial prediction. It is about conscious stewardship of your energy\, tim
 e\, and resources &mdash\; and building something that can last.\n\nWho Th
 is Is For\n\n    &bull\;    Entrepreneurs\, small business owners\, and cr
 eatives\n\n    &bull\;    Those navigating career transitions or expansion
 \n\n    &bull\;    Anyone redefining their relationship with money and wor
 th\n\n    &bull\;    Tarot beginners and experienced readers alike\n\nEart
 h teaches us that prosperity grows through care\, consistency\, and honest
  self-assessment. This gathering offers a supportive container to listen t
 o what your work and resources are asking of you &mdash\; and how to respo
 nd with clarity and confidence.
LOCATION:Magick Oak - Metaphysical Center & Enchanted Goods
URL:https://mynorthbaytickets.ticketsauce.com/e/tea-and-tarot-earth-busine
 ss-prosperity?aff=cityspark
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
