BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Growing Dahlias: Dividing & Planting for Success
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260421T103000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260421T123000
UID:26040193_YST4dRkSrO2rg_TC0cw
DESCRIPTION:Growing Dahlias: Dividing & Planting for Success\n\nLearn how 
 to grow healthy\, productive dahlias in your home garden. In this hands-on
  workshop\, local flower farmer Lisa Templeton of Lisa & Tula Flower Farm 
 will guide you through the essentials of planting and dividing dahlia tube
 rs.\n\nIn this workshop you’ll:\n\n• Learn how dahlias grow and reprod
 uce from tubers\n\n• Practice dividing tubers and identifying viable “
 eyes”\n\n• Understand planting depth\, spacing\, and support\n\n• Ex
 plore irrigation\, fertility\, and organic pest management\n\nEach partici
 pant will take home five tubers from Lisa’s collection to plant and grow
  in their own garden.\n\nPlease bring snips and gardening gloves.
LOCATION:Gather Sebastopol
URL:https://bohemian.com/events-calendar/#/details/growing-dahlias-dividin
 g-planting-for-success/18486310/2026-04-21T10
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
