DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260422T191500
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260422T201500
UID:260330_mGsn4Ofq0ieuy1ayZTuwg
DESCRIPTION:Ready to take your salsa to the next level? This 6-week salsa 
 intermediate series is designed for dancers who already know the basics \\
 (timing\, basic steps\, and simple turns\, etc.\\) and want to build the c
 onfidence and versatility to shine on the social dance floor.\n\nIn this c
 lass\, you’ll:\n\n• Develop adaptability so you can flow with differen
 t partners and music.\n\n• Refine your footwork and styling for sharper 
 expression.\n\n• Master more complex turn patterns and combinations.\n\n
 • Strengthen your lead and follow for smoother\, more connected dancing.
 \n\nWhat to Expect: Steven’s teaching style blends structure with fun\, 
 creating a supportive space where you’ll be challenged but never overwhe
 lmed. Each week builds on the last\, helping you progress steadily while k
 eeping the joy of salsa front and center.\n\nDetails:\n\n• No partner ne
 cessary — rotations ensure everyone gets to dance.\n\n• Please wear n
 on-marking shoe soles to protect the floor.\n\n• Arrive 10 minutes earl
 y to warm up and get settled.\n\nDate & Time: Wednesdays @ 7:15PM – 8:15
 PM\n\nInstructor: Steven Khuong\n\nAddress: 4140 Redwood Highway \\#8 San 
 Rafael\, CA
LOCATION:Salsa Dance Marin
URL:https://bohemian.com/events-calendar/#/details/salsa-intermediate-6wee
 ks/18461295/2026-04-22T19
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
