DESCRIPTION:Spirit Guides: Fantastical Creatures from the Workshop of Jaco
 bo and María Ángeles features brightly colored\, richly patterned sculp
 tures depicting imaginary hybrid animals that serve as spirit guides and a
 strological embodiments of human character. Inspired by the Zapotec calend
 ar\, the exhibition includes eight large-scale works organized by Denver B
 otanic Gardens.
