BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Salsa Beginners 2 - Thursdays
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260423T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260423T203000
UID:260407sEzNsrdG-kGq_T3HJLz71A
DESCRIPTION:Ready to take your salsa to the next level? You’ve mastered 
 the basics\, now it’s time to add some flair and fluidity to your salsa 
 dancing..\n\nPre-requisite: Salsa Beginners 1 – You know your basic step
 s\, left turn\, right turn\, cross-body lead\, and you hold your frame.\n\
 nWhat You’ll Learn\n\nWe’ve curated a curriculum designed to build you
 r confidence and your “social dance” vocabulary:\n\n• The Cross Body
  Lead \\(CBL\\) Series: Master both Inside and Outside Turns\, the essenti
 al building blocks for moving your partner across the floor with grace.\n\
 n• The “I Turn – You Turn”: A classic social dance staple that dev
 elops timing and hand-change coordination.\n\n• The Walk-Through: Learn 
 how to transition smoothly through the dance space without breaking your r
 hythm.\n\n• Footwork & Shine: We’ll break down the footwork pattern th
 at adds personality to your “shines.”\n\nTechnique & Artistry\n\nDanci
 ng is about more than just where your feet go. In this level\, we dive dee
 per into the “how”:\n\n• The Frame: Understand the “tension and co
 mpression” needed to lead and follow clearly without using muscle.\n\n
 • Upper Body Mechanics: Learn how to isolate your ribcage and shoulders 
 to move with that authentic Latin soul.\n\n• Connection: Developing a 
 “heavy” but responsive arm connection to ensure your partner feels eve
 ry lead.\n\nImportant Details\n\n• No dance experience required: Whether
  you’ve never danced before or it’s been a while\, you’re welcome he
 re!\n\n• No partner necessary: Come solo or bring a friend—either way\
 , you’ll have plenty of opportunities to dance.\n\n• Please wear non-m
 arking shoe soles: This helps us keep our dance floor in great condition.\
 n\nDate & Time:\n\nThursdays 7:30 PM\n\nSaturday 11:00 AM\n\nInstructor: L
 ucie Ebnerova\n\nAddress: 4140 Redwood Highway \\#8 San Rafael\, CA\n\nNot
 e: Arrive 10 minutes before. No floor marking shoe soles allowed.
LOCATION:Salsa Dance Marin
URL:https://bohemian.com/events-calendar/#/details/salsa-beginners-2-thurs
 days/18520306/2026-04-23T19
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
