DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260424T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260424T200000
UID:260331JYMfPUGR9Ee67AgCLWR24w
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a fun\, stress-free painting class where you’ll
  create your own masterpiece in just two hours! Follow along as the instr
 uctor paints a themed artwork on the easel\, and feel free to add your own
  personal touch. Each class features a different scene to paint\, making 
 each session unique. Whether you're a beginner or experienced\, the focu
