DESCRIPTION:Parents! Take an hour just for YOU—right before school pick-
 up! \\(Non-parent adults also welcome!\\)\n\nBring a yoga mat or blanket\,
  plus pillows and anything you need to be cozy\, then simply lie back as w
 aves of sound from crystal bowls\, chimes\, and gongs flow through you. No
  effort or experience needed. Like floating in an ocean of vibration\, the
  frequencies relieve stress\, calm your mind\, and restore energy at a cel
 lular level.\n\nYou’ll leave refreshed\, grounded\, and ready to greet y
 our kids and the weekend with patience\, presence\, and joy.
