DESCRIPTION:Boys & Girls Clubs of Sonoma-Marin is hosting their annual d
 inner & auction Healdsburg in Bloom. Join us Friday\, April 24th\, at 
 the historic Villa Chanticleer for an elegant evening that celebrates 
 22 years of community and nearly eight decades of service to Healdsbur
 g youth. \n\nWe are proud to honor our roots while raising vital funds fo
 r after-school and summer programs supporting over 400 local children in
  Healdsburg—where great futures begin to bloom. Guests will enjoy an e
 vening of connecting with others passionate about empowering youth and a
  world-class culinary experience catered by the renowned Troubadour Bread
  & Bistro\, paired with exquisite local wines and high-energy auctions. \
 n\nAll proceeds will benefit the Boys & Girls Clubs of Sonoma-Marin 
 to support life-changing programs for local youth.  \n\n Learn how to s
