DESCRIPTION:Join us on April 24\, 2026 as we kick off the best weekend of 
 2026 in Wine Country! Chef Kevin O'Connor of Hulu&'s Chefs vs. Wild\, and 
 his team\, will be back for the 2nd year to heat things up at Bacchus Land
 ing with their thoughtfully planned & executed open-fire cooking! DJ Saint
  Rose Disco plans to keep the vibes high all evening with epic beats while
  you sip & savor wines from 20\\+ Dry Creek Valley wineries! Make sure to 
 dress in your best denim on denim! This Twilight Welcome Party is going to
  be a festive evening you won't want to miss & the perfect start to a fabu
 lous weekend! You're supporting the legacy of our agriculture\, our story 
 and our non-profit organization - celebrating the valley\, its wineries\, 
 farmers\, grape growers and community! Although we'd love for you to join 
 us for all of Passport weekend\, you don't need to in order to join us Fri
 day night. Experience sip to soil - taste the land.
LOCATION:Bacchus Landing
URL:https://cm.healdsburg.com/events/details/twilight-welcome-party-passpo
 rt-to-dry-creek-valley-23077
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
