BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Stand-up + Improv = STANDPROV | Downtown Santa Rosa Good Times
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260425T200000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260425T220000
UID:260404xs4R5KNbgE22t_LnXQ5BPg
DESCRIPTION:Get ready for a night of hilarious stand-up comedy and spontan
 eous improv at STANDPROV in Downtown Santa Rosa - it's gonna be a blast!\n
 \nStand-up + Improv = STANDPROV | Downtown Santa Rosa Good Time\n\nTake pa
 rt in a truly unique comedy experience! Equal parts standup and improvisat
 ional comedy\, StandProv electrifies audiences who enjoy spontaneous acts 
 of comedic re-interpretation.\n\nWith a blend aging like only the finest o
 f wines (four years)\, the StandProv concoction mixes stand-up comedy and 
 improv sourced from the best of Northern California comedians and improvis
 ers. StandProv frankensteins together the best parts of standup and improv
  comedy. Standup comedians perform their most time-tested bits\, which the
 n become the inspiration for a cast of improvisers to build out characters
 \, scenes\, and premises. Pairing non-stop entertainment with good vibes d
 istills the balanced portmanteau commonly referred to in layman's terms as
  StandProv .\n\nFeaturing premier Bay Area comedians and improvisers\, Sta
 ndProv offers a uniquely familiar performance experience to fans of standu
 p\, improv\, and experimental art-form fusions alike!\n\nApril's performer
 s include: - Marcus Peverill - Scott Powers - Brendan Caskey - Gina Maycli
 n - Josh Jobrack - Katie Lindsey - Rachel Pyle\n\nHosted By:\n\nFranco Tev
 ini\n\nA talented standup comedian and host of StandProv \, Franco perform
 s digestible bits of surreal\, elevated slice-of-life comedy.\n\nJeremy Le
 ssnau\n\nA Sonoma county based improvisational comedian/musician\, who co-
 hosts StandProv as equal parts passion-project and court-ordered community
  service.\n\nIf you're looking for a memorable night of rofl-worthy laught
 er\, check out StandProv at Barrel Proof Lounge in downtown Santa Rosa\, S
 aturday\, April 25th!\n\nVIP TABLES NOW AVAILABLE! Snag a table for 4 with
  preferred seating\, your own private call button to summon service\, and 
 your first round of drinks (or a bottle of wine) for only $95!\n\n21+ Door
 s @7/Show @8 $15adv / $20door\n\n"Equal parts standup and improvisational 
 comedy\, StandProv electrifies audiences who enjoy a laugh of any kind"\n\
 nCheck out **www.BarrelProofLounge.com** for all sorts of good times ahe
 ad!
LOCATION:Barrel Proof Lounge
URL:https://www.eventbrite.com/e/stand-up-improv-standprov-downtown-santa-
 rosa-good-times-tickets-1986559411677?aff=oddtdtcreator
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
