DESCRIPTION:Get crafty and sip your fave drink while making stunning faux 
 stained glass art together!\n\nJoin Us for **Craft & Sip: Faux Stained Gl
 ass**!\n\nGet ready for a fun\, crafty afternoon where you can **create s
 tunning faux stained glass art** while enjoying some good vibes. This **
 in-person** event is perfect for anyone looking to unwind and let their c
 reativity flow. No experience needed\, just bring your imagination and a s
 mile! Whether you're a craft pro or a newbie\, you'll leave with a beautif
 ul piece and great memories.\n\nAll materials included \n\nArrive a littl
