BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:West Marin Impressions  Natural Egg Dyeing Workshop
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260425T130000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260425T153000
UID:260327bzezSG26eUWUoqaCGNxKJg
DESCRIPTION:Venture to West Main to step into the country to experiment wi
 th eggs\, natural dyes and sketch some of the enchanting views found at *
 *Black Mountain Ranch**. Together we will explore and turn everyday items 
 into creative expressions.\n\n**Connect the Dots Art Studio** is bringing
  an ag-and eco-based inquiry-driven\, hands-on egg dying workshop to **Bl
 ack Mountain Ranch**—and you are invited to get creative with the artist
 s/educators from Connect the Dots who specialize in making art experiences
  engaging\, accessible\, and unforgettable. Using **Natural Egg Dye** you
  will use plants to stencil designs onto eggs. **Red cabbage** and **ye
 llow onions** will turn into robin egg-blue and toasty cinnamon colors th
 at are sure to please the palette. You’ll be directed on how to draw som
 e **West Marin** plants and turn your creations into labels for the jam j
 ars for you to transport your goods home safely.\n\n**Black Mountain Ranch
 ** and its expert ranch hands will take you on a guided hike that include
 s **breath-taking views** of West Marin and a visit to the pond. You’l
 l explore the barnyard to see the sheep and alpacas. The **three-story ba
 rn** doubles as an event space and includes a must-see **Wool Studio**. 
 A light **charcuterie board** will please the senses and keep the energy 
 going strong throughout the afternoon.\n\nAll participants will make art
 —they’ll observe\, question\, experiment\, and connect creativity to e
 co and ag-based awareness and creations. Expect curiosity\, collaboration\
 , and plenty of “whoa\, that worked?!” moments.\n\nDon’t miss out\; 
 sign up soon because spots are limited and expected to fill fast! Your tic
 ket includes all the necessary supplies. Sorry\, no refunds. Please wear c
 omfortable walking shoes. Enjoy plenty of free parking. No pets\, it’s a
  working ranch.\n\nBy the end of the afternoon\, everyone will take home t
 heir own egg-cellent creations—and you’ll be invited to share your cre
 ations online using **#connectthedotsartstudo** and **#blackmountainran
 ch**.
LOCATION:Black Mountain Ranch
URL:https://www.blackmountainranch.info/
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
