UID:260216ai28amlCBE-KevjZMb6MDg
DESCRIPTION:The family-favorite Flavors of Film: Family Series returns wit
 h a brand-new global twist! This season\, we invite you to join us every f
 ourth Sunday from February 22 through May 31 to explore different cultu
 res and corners of the world through a curated lineup of exciting films a
 nd interactive\, food-based experiences that bring each movie to life. 
 \n\nOur third stop will be in Mexico with the visually stunning film\,
  *Coco*. Following the screening\, there will be hands-on activities in
 spired by Mexican food\, culture\, and traditions\, bringing the film’s
  vibrant world to life. This immersive experience is a beautiful way to ex
 plore heritage\, creativity\, and connectivity that will leave a lasti
 ng impression.
