DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260426T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260426T150000
UID:260205eb2ValXs506ETQf3ELxB2Q
DESCRIPTION:The Sonoma County Wildfire & Earthquake Expo is a free\, famil
 y-friendly event designed to help kids and families learn how to stay safe
  and prepared during emergencies. Taking place on April 26\, 2026\, at the
  Sonoma County Event Center\, the Expo features hands-on activities\, inte
 ractive exhibits\, and engaging demonstrations led by first responders\, l
 ocal agencies\, and community organizations—making emergency preparednes
 s fun\, approachable\, and empowering for all ages.
LOCATION:Sonoma County Event Center at the Fairgrounds
URL:https://www.fireandearthquakeexpo.org/
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
