SUMMARY:Clear Horizons: Works by Peter Hassen
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260426T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260426T160000
UID:260401N-zzVxvY30qkAC9kJyP81w
DESCRIPTION:After more than three decades as a working artist in Sonoma an
 d across the North Bay\, Peter Hassen will mark the end of a chapter with 
 a special two-day studio event\, Clear Horizons: Works by Peter Hassen\, A
 pril 25-26 from 10 AM to 4 PM at his White Barn Studio \\(900 Petaluma Ave
 .\, Sonoma\\). Known for his sculptural work and public art projects-inclu
 ding installations on Sonoma Plaza and participation in the Napa Art Walk-
 Hassen has been an active part of the region's creative community. As he p
 repares to relocate to Spain\, the event offers collectors and the broader
  arts community a rare opportunity to view a wide selection of works from 
 throughout his career.
URL:https://creativesonoma.org/event/clear-horizons-works-by-peter-hassen/
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
