DESCRIPTION:Celebrate local business at the Santa Rosa Metro Expo! The San
 ta Rosa Metro Expo\, the Chamber’s largest and most interactive networki
 ng event and business expo\, is a powerful branding tool\, giving you the 
 opportunity to place your products\, services\, and staff in front of hund
 reds of business and community leaders. 3 hours\, over 100 local exhibitor
 s\, endless opportunities to connect! Averaging nearly 1\,000 attendees\, 
 the Santa Rosa Metro Expo is the place to meet local Sonoma County busines
 s people one-on-one and to be introduced to new business in our metro area
 . This year\, the event falls on April 28th — National Superhero Day —
  a perfect reminder that Sonoma County businesses are the true superheroes
  keeping our local economy thriving. Become an exhibitor Take advantage of
  the B2B and B2C opportunities by joining over 100 fellow Sonoma County bu
 sinesses — from tech\, finance\, and services to restaurants\, wineries\
 , and breweries. No-cost food/beer/wine booths A limited number of no-cost
  food/beer/wine exhibitor booths are also available for exhibitors who wou
 ld like to showcase tastes of their products. Become a sponsor A select nu
 mber of sponsorships are available that will showcase your brand to the re
 gion’s top influencers and decision-makers\, start-ups\, and entrepreneu
 rs\, while offering publicity and promotion to the wider public. The Santa
  Rosa Metro Expo is open to the public.
LOCATION:Luther Burbank Center for the Arts
URL:https://www.facebook.com/events/2503283126798319/
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
