 in any of its policies\, procedures or practices\; nor does the District d
 iscriminate against any employees or applicants for employment on the basi
 s of their age. This non-discrimination policy covers admission\, access a
 nd treatment in District programs and activities--including but not limite
 d to academic admissions\, financial aid\, educational services and athlet
 ics--and application for District employment.
