DESCRIPTION:Checkmate Your Thursday Nights at CUVER Join us every Thursday
  at 6:30 PM for the CUVER Chess Club!\n\nIf you’re looking for a fresh c
 hallenge or just a friendly place to play\, you’ve found it. We pair the
  timeless game of chess with the relaxed atmosphere of a craft brewery. No
  experience? No problem. We’re a welcoming community where everyone—fr
 om kids to pros—can enjoy a match.\n\nDetails:\n\nWhen: Thursdays @ 6:30
  PM\n\nWhere: CUVER Brewery\n\nNote: All ages welcome. No purchase necessa
 ry. Refreshing craft beer and NA beverages are available!
LOCATION:CUVER Belgian Brewers
URL:http://cuverbrewing.com
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
