 ork’s Wine Down happy hour.\n\nEarly evenings of wine\, conversation\, a
 nd community bring together local makers\, artists\, small business owners
 \, startups\, and anyone curious about the neighborhood. Meet fellow membe
 rs\, discover what everyone actually does here\, and enjoy a relaxed\, w
 arm atmosphere. Bring a friend - members or not\, everyone is welcome.\n\n
 Whether you’re new in town or a longtime local\, let the wine\, conversa
 tion\, and gentle hum of Healdsburg carry you into an evening of connectio
 n and community.\n\nMore about us: www.craftworkhbg.com
LOCATION:CraftWork Healdsburg
